            <title>[PIG-3071] update hcatalog jar and path to hbase storage handler jar in pig script</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3071</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Due to changes in hcatalog 0.5 packaging we need to update the hcatalog jar name and the path to the hbase storage handler jar. We also need to add the pig storage adapter to the class path&lt;/p&gt;

